	<name>Perfidix Project</name>
	<version>3.6.2</version>
	<description>Perfidix comes as a light-weight Java Benchmarking Tool which allows to make simple measurements of source code without intsalling heavy profilers or using special IDEs. Perfidix comes as a simple jar which has to be included in the classpath. Methods which should be benched are annotated similar to JUnit testcases. With these simple modifications  fast evaluation and real-time measurements can be made with existing source code without adapting the program.</description>
